headline: Darden Restaurants to Host Fiscal 2025 Third Quarter Conference Call on March 20
summary: Darden Restaurants, Inc., (NYSE: DRI) plans to release its fiscal 2025 third quarter financial results before the market opens on Thursday, March 20, 2025, with a conference call to follow at 8:30 am ET. Rick Cardenas, CEO, and other senior management will discuss third quarter results and conduct a question and answer session. For those who cannot listen to the live broadcast, a replay will be available shortly after the call.
